<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.4.1">
<l>canta malarkkuḻal tāḻat tāṉukan tōṭit taṉiyē</l>
<l>vanteṉ mulaittaṭan taṉṉai vāṅkiniṉ vāyil maṭuttu</l>
<l>nantaṉ peṟappeṟṟa  nampī nāṉukan tuṇṇu mamutē</l>
<l>yentai perumaṉē yuṇṇā yeṉṉammam cēma muṇṇāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As curls with colorful flowers hang down, happily running coming alone,</l>
<l>Taking the fullness of my breasts, sucking with your lips,</l>
<l>Prince whom Nanda got to obtain, nectar which I happily relish,</l>
<l>Father, great lord, suckle; suckle the treasure of my milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
